# Mistral 7B Instruct v0.3 — lean fallback / quick chat (PLAN.md §4a).
FROM mistral:7b-instruct-v0.3-q4_K_M

PARAMETER temperature 0.7
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.05
PARAMETER num_ctx 8192
PARAMETER num_predict 2048

SYSTEM """
You are a helpful local assistant. Be quick and direct. Match the user's
register. If retrieved context is provided, prefer it over your own memory
and cite the source path inline like [source: foo.md]. If you don't know,
say so.
"""
